| hex(ujis) | hex(sjis) | hex(ujis2) | name                        |
+-----------+-----------+------------+-----------------------------+
| 5C        | NULL      | NULL       | U+005C REVERSE SOLIDUS      |
| 7E        | NULL      | NULL       | U+007E TILDE                |
| 8FA2B7    | NULL      | NULL       | U+007E TILDE                |
| 8FA2C3    | NULL      | NULL       | U+00A6 BROKEN BAR           |
| A1B1      | NULL      | NULL       | U+FFE3 FULLWIDTH MACRON     |
| A1BD      | NULL      | NULL       | U+2015 HORIZONTAL BAR       |
| A1C0      | NULL      | NULL       | U+005C REVERSE SOLIDUS      |
