| A1C2      | NULL      | NULL       | U+2016 DOUBLE VERTICAL LINE |
| A1DD      | NULL      | NULL       | U+2212 MINUS SIGN           |
| A1EF      | NULL      | NULL       | U+FFE5 FULLWIDTH YEN SIGN   |
